name: A Lost Kitten The Adventures of Charlies Cat Back Home
name_original: A Lost Kitten The Adventures of Charlies Cat Back Home
description:
Get the lost kitten as far up the block as you can.

She is lost and wants to go home, help her out. Charlie will eat milk, meat, and fish. So be careful to collect those items. She can also boost her powers by collecting other items, like the little angel statue.

Be aware of the flappy birds that can kill you. There's also a bad lady that throws dead fishes at you.

Flowerpots are not your friends, so stay away from them. Don't jump on them, don't get too close.

Take mister Charlie home or as far up the block.

There's a long way, and you're the only one who can help!

I mean, IF you can!
